on system evolution in the wild.</gtr:description><gtr:exploitationPathways>To discover how Wolbachia interacts with is host, useful in control of vector competence</gtr:exploitationPathways><gtr:id>4F7CAA57-03D0-4C3D-8CB3-7710271546F7</gtr:id><gtr:sectors><gtr:sector>Agriculture, Food and Drink,Environment</gtr:sector></gtr:sectors></gtr:keyFindingsOutput><gtr:otherResearchOutputs/><gtr:policyInfluenceOutputs><gtr:policyInfluenceOutput><gtr:areas/><gtr:description>BES</gtr:description><gtr:geographicReach>National</gtr:geographicReach><gtr:id>8767DFFA-3091-427E-88D5-AA71FA096D78</gtr:id><gtr:impact>Member of BES Education committee, advising on changes in GCSE and A level curricula to Department of Education through SCORE</gtr:impact><gtr:type>Membership of a guidance committee</gtr:type><gtr:url>http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201213/cmselect/cmeduc/141/141we22.htm</gtr:url></gtr:policyInfluenceOutput></gtr:policyInfluenceOutputs><gtr:productOutputs/><gtr:researchDatabaseAndModelOutputs><gtr:researchDatabaseAndModelOutput><gtr:description>Short read data for Hypolimnas transcriptome</gtr:description><gtr:id>C19575C5-D513-40B4-90FF-61F0F090C167</gtr:id><gtr:impact>Paper in PloS Genetics</gtr:impact><gtr:providedToOthers>true</gtr:providedToOthers><gtr:title>Hypolimnasshortreads</gtr:title><gtr:type>Database/Collection of data</gtr:type><gtr:url>http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/bioproject/259306</gtr:url><gtr:yearFirstProvided>2014</gtr:yearFirstProvided></gtr:researchDatabaseAndModelOutput></gtr:researchDatabaseAndModelOutputs><gtr:researchMaterialOutputs/><gtr:softwareAndTechnicalProductOutputs/><gtr:spinOutOutputs/></gtr:output><gtr:publications><gtr:publication url="http://gtr.rcuk.ac.uk:80/publication/AAFB86C2-7C01-49CB-BDC6-AB0F699CF0FA"><gtr:id>AAFB86C2-7C01-49CB-BDC6-AB0F699CF0FA</gtr:id><gtr:title>The evolution of sex ratio distorter suppression affects a 25 cM genomic region in the butterfly Hypolimnas bolina.</gtr:title><gtr:parentPublicationTitle>P